These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, apricot
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, lily
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra
1. the swisher-smoker is not to the right of the person who growslily##8
2. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
3. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Color      | apricot     | brown      |
| Flower          | lily | daffodil    |
| Pet         | pony   | rabbit |
| Cigar   | swisher  | alhambra      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
House: modern, townhouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, baseball
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, d&b
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, peach
1. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
3. the fan of d&b is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
4. the person eating cauliflower is not the person who's sport is baseball##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| House    | modern        | townhouse    |
| Sport       | rowing         | baseball |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | techno   |
| Food   | cauliflower               | peach  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different games are played: billiard, canasta
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, pilot
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, september
1. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
3. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game   | billiard       | canasta |
| Job   | fisherman       | pilot    |
| Flower   | daisy | bellflower |
| Birthday           | june        | september   |

