There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda
1. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
2. the person eating pepper is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Food         | onion | pepper  |
| Cigar           | game  | alhambra |
| Flower   | azalea | sunflower   |
| Beverage     | mirinda   | hot-chocolate |

